room_title: Escape room "Sorcerer's Secret" by Mastermind Escape Games in Overland Park
room_description: After your uncle's mysterious disappearance, you arrive at his magic shop to search the last place he was seen for clues. Maybe this has something to do with his rival, the evil Sorcerer? As soon as you enter, the Sorcerer's curse befalls you, and now you have only 60 minutes left to break the curse and escape the magic lair.
